Text::Template::Simple
======================

A simple template class mainly for web applications.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires this other module:

	Text::Template 1.44

Which is available on CPAN.

